children.subject: Math 110 is probably not necessarily considering how well he did in Math 54 and EE16a imo

In my opinion, if you did well in both cs70 and math 54 then you are set to go. CS 61C is the easiest from the CS61 series and CS 170 relies on cs70 material. CS 189 is regarded as a challenging class but if you handle the workload well I don't see why you cannot succeed.
